You should also know =E2=80=93 because I hear you thinking =E2=80=9CThis mu=
st be punishingly capital intensive=E2=80=9D =E2=80=93 that Cuby licenses e=
ach MMF via Special Purpose Vehicles (SPVs) with local partner/operators, o=
