nt-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Then you&#8217;re go=
ing to need to internalize a ton of complexity &#8211; just the right amoun=
t, at the right level of integration &#8211; and make it feel simple to the=
 thousands of individual parties involved in the process.&#160;</p><p style=
=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;"><span>Cuby&#8217;s goal is to help </span><em>others</em><span> b=
uild as many square feet of housing as they can with as few hours of skille=
d labor as possible.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); fo=
nt-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>The first ques=
tion to ask, the answer which is not as obvious as it seems, is what produc=
t it&#8217;s building to achieve that goal. If early prefab companies&#8217=
; products were homes, and Katerra&#8217;s product was materials, </span><s=
