n: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;"><strong>Quality:</strong><span>=
 By using steel framing and non-structural insulated sandwich panels, Cuby =
can produce homes that are more durable and energy-efficient than typical s=
tick-built houses.</span></p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p st=
yle=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; lin=
e-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;"><strong>La=
bor Efficiency:</strong><span> This is the bottleneck that everything is de=
signed to solve.&#160;</span></p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><=
p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px;=
 line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;"><stron=
g>Customization:</strong><span> Despite the standardized process, Cuby's sy=
stem allows for hundreds of permutations in terms of size, layout, and fini=
shes.</span></p></li></ol><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16=
px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The result is a product that lo=
