hat otherwise would have been generated on typical construction sites, and =
reduce 2.2 million tons of CO2.&#8221;</strong></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(5=
4, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The wh=
