el like traditional construction, but they're built faster and potentially =
cheaper. By offering asymmetric upside (significant cost savings) for minim=
al perceived risk, they're creating a strong incentive for adoption.</p><p =
style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin=
