t conversation, he told me they&#8217;d just signed a term sheet with the d=
eveloper. </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-hei=
ght: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">To win in this space, you have to offer uni=
